                <h1>Explore Hades: The Greek God of the Underworld</h1>
                <p>Hades is the ancient Greek god of the underworld, ruling over the realm of the dead. He governs the afterlife and ensures that souls are given their due. Often misunderstood, Hades symbolizes the inevitability of death rather than evil. He is also associated with wealth, as the earth's minerals and treasures belong to him.</p>
